S|# 24 · Cinematic Sites (Revenue)|> The client-website build offering — "cinematic" sites produced for clients (e.g. Maria's new collection), a productized deliverable of the consulting business.
S|Purpose|A revenue module for building **cinematic client websites**. It surfaces in the dec Queue/Inbox as the "Cinematic site for the new collection — timeline?" inquiry from **Maria (Brightwave Studio)** worth ~€5k, and in Asset Lab as "Cinematic Site hero — Maria project." This page is where such site projects are tracked and produced.
S|What it covers (inferred + cross-referenced)|- A list/board of **client site projects** with status (inquiry → scoped → in prd → delivered). // - Per-project assets pulled from **Asset Lab** (cinematic hero imagery, e.g. "dusk skyline") generated by Leonardo. // - Likely ties into the **Software pl** (Nexus builds/deploys via Vercel) for the actual site code and the **Consulting CRM** for the commercial side. // - Example live project: **Maria / Brightwave Studio** — new collection cinematic site, ~€5k, timeline being negotiated over email
S|Relationship to other screens|- Commercial pl in **Consulting CRM** (`23`); client comms in **Email Inbox** (`25`) and **dec Queue** (`01`). // - Visual assets from **Asset Lab** (`19`); build/deploy via **Software pl** (`22`). // > **Confidence:** Listed in the sidebar (REVENUE) and concretely referenced (Maria's cinematic site appears in Inbox, dec Queue and Asset Lab), but not shown as a dedicated screen. Structure above is *inferred* from those references.